Enchanter

Focus: Conjuring based magic, trade, utility

Roleplay: Enchanters are one of the common mage types found in most
cities. They are more focused on helpful spells and spells that create
things. Their skill set reflects this, providing the Enchanter with the 
ability to mine, farm and sell their wares. They can be found in most 
places where magic is practiced, such as libraries.

Diffuculty: Moderate